"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"> ### 引言\\n>\\n> *本文为 Stablecoin DeFi策略系列第 3 篇，系列其它策略如下：*\\n>\\n> * *[$UST-$Mirror策略（Terra链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/b6PnhUTzoHF4_sywNXtC8OfZoZYM1gGDj22e7tpHplU)*\\n> * *[$UST-$MIM策略（ETH链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/Oz3Sdd4D5JZTZ3b13ABAaL2WjWi6_IQRDRjGH-jZtZI)*\\n> * *[$FTM-$TOMB策略（Fantom链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/rlWkMMbg2H9GlsuFVXAwyjfRu4gkcfYjNia7wAbbhRc)*\\n> * *[$ATOM-$OSMO策略（Cosmos链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/hAX73I66TcUTc5gCHbrjJ6vhor3Pi07fhtKMb9cw4Qo)*\\n> * *[$TIME Staking策略（Avalance链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/br12Nt9v13oMGoN1fv1PWt3oX5uAY89DUbqbf8PQJ88)*\\n> * *[稳定币 DeFi协议总结](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/vjhrsKgkRRA4B9cf7Sb5FpfKHziM7ckdzhqmBxLAvlg)*\\n>\\n> *其中涉及到的操作指南如下：*\\n>\\n> * *[$UST跨链指南（ETH链）](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/U5HcyR431ID0WwFItQa5k698jAzy3VBDtD-2ks-xYKM)*\\n\\n### 一、准备$FTM到Metamask（Fantom链）\\n\\n1. 在CEX（如Coinbase、Binance、Huobi等）上买入$BUSD，闪兑换成$FTM（1 BUSD = 0.778452 FTM）；\\n2. 提现到MetaMask（FTM钱包），$FTM链，手续费低；\\n\\n### 二、到spookyswap组合LP\\n\\n1. 到[spookyswap.finance](https://spookyswap.finance/)，点击上方「Swap」，兑换50%的$FTM，换成$TOMB，手续费$0.5；\\n2. 点击上方「Liquidity」，进入[「+Supply」](https://spookyswap.finance/add)页面，选50%的$FTM，和50%的$TOMB，组合 FTM-TOMB LP，确认两次，手续费低（最多$0.5）；\\n\\n### 三、准备$FTM到Metamask（Fantom链）\\n\\n1. 到 [reaper.farm](https://www.reaper.farm/)，链接 MM 钱包，选 Fantom链；\\n2. 找到 $FTM-$TOMB-pool，先认证LP，再点击「Deposit」存入，当前收益为365.174119%；\\n3. 后续可以直接到[stake](https://www.reaper.farm/staked)页面，点击「More Info」查看当前收益；\\n4. `作者参考：Year Yield-1374.400%；`\\n\\n### 五、收益再投入\\n\\n1. $FTM-$TOMB组合收到$TSHARE；\\n2. `作者参考：$TSHARE (259% APR = 1417% APY)，$TSHARE市价 $11,270；`\\n3. 如果有多的$FTM，可以组合TSHARE:FTM (472% APR = 10,782% APY)，收到$TSHARE再组合；\\n4. 或者单边抵押$TSHARE；\\n5. 确认交易。\\n\\n### 六、结束\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2BnA0pQiMgLbRco-UB1dX.jpeg?height=900&width=1600)\\n\\n## 策略汇总：\\n\\n## Terra(🌍,🌍)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/b6PnhUTzoHF4_sywNXtC8OfZoZYM1gGDj22e7tpHplU](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/b6PnhUTzoHF4_sywNXtC8OfZoZYM1gGDj22e7tpHplU)\\n\\n## Ethereum(Ξ,Ξ)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/Oz3Sdd4D5JZTZ3b13ABAaL2WjWi6_IQRDRjGH-jZtZI](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/Oz3Sdd4D5JZTZ3b13ABAaL2WjWi6_IQRDRjGH-jZtZI)\\n\\n## Fantom(👻,👻)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/rlWkMMbg2H9GlsuFVXAwyjfRu4gkcfYjNia7wAbbhRc](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/rlWkMMbg2H9GlsuFVXAwyjfRu4gkcfYjNia7wAbbhRc)\\n\\n## Cosmos(⚛️,⚛️)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/hAX73I66TcUTc5gCHbrjJ6vhor3Pi07fhtKMb9cw4Qo](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/hAX73I66TcUTc5gCHbrjJ6vhor3Pi07fhtKMb9cw4Qo)\\n\\n## Avalance(🎩,🎩)\\n\\n[https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/br12Nt9v13oMGoN1fv1PWt3oX5uAY89DUbqbf8PQJ88](https://mirror.xyz/kishibe.eth/br12Nt9v13oMGoN1fv1PWt3oX5uAY89DUbqbf8PQJ88)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641203466,\"title\":\"$FTM-$TOMB策略（👻，🪦）\"},\"digest\":\"kNm7Zq3AdbUCiPKU-McQ_StSjyv_qzCeKYrhZi9O2no\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x2caAfafBc21f65697824f83aEAe6A9b1CB2a5B9D\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SkVV_-Xl3k90FjwbifpvhCPhuiYzJWPRe2rXCGV2qRg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"AbCKotboCHNs6i9ApRJjBG7aQ6hUIVAR6yF-kgNSMH4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"QXL_tgMTtsP7V-hzRkV8Ksvndk4GLKENwn4TlqfHozgmE8fkmcuZ37GHTkAviUTLwSedXJwZhYU0ywckw43h2w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xda5f1efe4c865be0f788eb7e7b166fd1f844e7f25aabb8713c46c2f05fe51695139aa85c3a7ae92e9481acb089405a35acb46181e57966fc9a492d23caad16551c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SkVV_-Xl3k90FjwbifpvhCPhuiYzJWPRe2rXCGV2qRg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"AbCKotboCHNs6i9ApRJjBG7aQ6hUIVAR6yF-kgNSMH4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"rlWkMMbg2H9GlsuFVXAwyjfRu4gkcfYjNia7wAbbhRc\"}"